    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to a world where bunnies aren't just cute—they're your key to victory!</strong> <br><br>In this fast-paced, score-chasing adventure, your goal is simple: eat as many bunnies as you can to rack up points and dominate the leader board. But beware—these bunnies get stronger the deeper you go, offering greater rewards but also tougher challenges. <br><br><strong>Will you rise to the top by devouring the fiercest bunnies and claiming the highest score? <br>It’s time to find out—happy hunting!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198260/extras/218bd7a81313df7476cbfa67a164d392.avif?t=1728903125\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt as many bunnies you can before the day cycle ends.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198260/extras/9060db4f96bdc7e73a1cf0634b47175b.avif?t=1728903125\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid incoming attacks from stronger bunnies, survive as long as possible during your hunt runs. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198260/extras/dde45423e7614d0711b3b9360d052c85.avif?t=1728903125\" width=600 height=94 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find potions that aid you with abilities such as invisibility and faster movement.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
